{"id":702070,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edgardo_Mesa","text":"Edgardo Mesa (29 December 1937 \u2013 25 June 2019) was an Argentine actor, journalist and radio broadcaster. He was born in Pergamino, Argentina. Mesa worked for Radio Mitre, Radio El Mundo, Radio Rivadavia, Radio Continental, Concordia and Entre R\u00EDos.\nAn actor, he was known for his roles in \"Los reyes del sablazo\", \"Rambito y Ramb\u00F3n, primera misi\u00F3n\", \"Los colimbas se divierten\", \"Brigada explosiva contra los ninjas\", \"Los colimbas al ataque\", \"Galer\u00EDa del terror\", \"Atracci\u00F3n peculiar\" and \"Pacto de silencio\".\nMesa died at a Buenos Aires hospital on 25 June 2019 from emphysema at the age of 81.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Pergamino","surface_form":"Pergamino","offset":120},{"uri":"Radio_Mitre","surface_form":"Radio Mitre","offset":158},{"uri":"Radio_El_Mundo","surface_form":"Radio El Mundo","offset":171},{"uri":"Radio_Rivadavia","surface_form":"Radio Rivadavia","offset":187},{"uri":"Radio_Continental","surface_form":"Radio Continental","offset":204},{"uri":"Concordia_(Argentina)","surface_form":"Concordia","offset":223},{"uri":"Entre_R%C3%ADos","surface_form":"Entre R\u00EDos","offset":237},{"uri":"Los_reyes_del_sablazo","surface_form":"Los reyes del sablazo","offset":290},{"uri":"Rambito_y_Ramb%C3%B3n%2C_primera_misi%C3%B3n","surface_form":"Rambito y Ramb\u00F3n, primera misi\u00F3n","offset":315},{"uri":"Los_colimbas_se_divierten","surface_form":"Los colimbas se divierten","offset":351},{"uri":"Brigada_explosiva_contra_los_ninjas","surface_form":"Brigada explosiva contra los ninjas","offset":380},{"uri":"Los_colimbas_al_ataque","surface_form":"Los colimbas al ataque","offset":419},{"uri":"Galer%C3%ADa_del_terror","surface_form":"Galer\u00EDa del terror","offset":445},{"uri":"Atracci%C3%B3n_peculiar","surface_form":"Atracci\u00F3n peculiar","offset":467},{"uri":"Pacto_de_silencio","surface_form":"Pacto de silencio","offse